1. What books do you like to read? — We like to read different books. 2. Do you
speak the English or the German language to your friends? — We usually speak
English. 3. I like these flowers very much. 4. Who buys milk? — Our grandmother
buys milk. 5. Who is there? — This is Ann. 6. Does your son watch many films on
TV? — He usually watches many films. 7. What does he often write? — He often
writes letters. 8. Where do you live? — I live in Berlin. Berlin is a very big city. I live
in the center of the city. 9. We learn the French language. We read books. 10. Do you
read many books? - We read many books now. 11. I do not like the new film.
